{"tid":1303154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得「社會信用評級系統」係好恐怖","createTime":"2019-07-10T08:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T08:11:54.000Z","uid":274858,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14c25bd472b3c4b50980947280c566000b04e44e","tid":1303154,"uid":274858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:06:04.000Z","msg":"啱啱重溫咗一次黑鏡(s3ep1)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MoJ2pYh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMoJ2pYh.png&h=760750f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前睇嘅時候冇咁大感覺 但係當知道呢樣野有機會係香港實行 有種好心寒嘅感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係生活好微細嘅事已經可以令你喺呢個社會失去存在嘅價值 分數一直扣 朋友開始遠離你 份工都冇埋 交通工具、機場員工唔再serve你 連離開呢個地方嘅自由都冇埋。<br />\n更令我恐懼嘅係 故事入邊反抗嘅人幾乎係冇 因為根本冇反抗嘅資本 你可能連搭港鐵入閘去金鐘遊行嘅資格都被取消 <span style=\"color: red;\">所以 香港人 大家用我哋僅餘嘅自由守住香港 多啲同身邊嘅人宣傳呢樣咁恐佈嘅系統 我哋已經冇嘢可以輸</span>"},{"pid":"252ce9c331bea9ee28c89b4b272b50700202d889","tid":1303154,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:06:27.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79fc463f95f83b47d5d45761a269fb3e8ada469c","tid":1303154,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>反大灣區一國一制融合 !!!</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">由小處到大局，逃犯條例的真面目。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1228296/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1228296/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">盧偉聰已鋪路，香港警隊將歸大灣區管！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1292683/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1292683/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港點解會變軍政府？詳細解說</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1296